Project Description

This project analyzes cricket tournament data using Excel.
The system collects match, team, and player statistics from multiple worksheets.
It processes the data using formulas, pivot tables, and charts to create an interactive dashboard.
The dashboard helps in understanding team performance, player statistics, and overall tournament trends.
